# Quality Gates

Her PR bu eşikleri karşılamalı. CI otomatik kontrol eder; merge blocked.

## Test Coverage Thresholds (Risk-Based)

Modül bazında hedefler:

| Risk seviyesi | Modüller | Line | Branch | Function |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| **Yüksek** | auth, encryption, permission-resolver, workflow engine, audit | ≥90% | ≥85% | 100% |
| **Orta** | users, roles, tasks, documents, notifications | 75-85% | 65-75% | 85-90% |
| **Düşük** | master-data CRUD, admin settings, UI components | 60-70% | 50-60% | 70-80% |
| **Overall backend** | — | ≥80% | ≥70% | ≥85% |
| **Overall frontend** | — | ≥75% | ≥65% | ≥80% |
| **Proje toplam** | CI gate | ≥75% | ≥65% | ≥80% |

Coverage eşiklerin altı → PR block. Yeni dosya coverage %70 altında ise warning (reviewer decision).

Coverage sayıları **proxy**, doğruluğun kendisi değil. %95 mock-heavy test zayıftır. Reviewer assertion kalitesine de bakar (trivial `toBeDefined()` vs davranış doğrulama).

## Test Türü Dağılımı (Piramit)

- **%70 unit** — Vitest, mock external deps, business logic real
- **%20 integration** — Vitest + testcontainers (PostgreSQL + Redis Docker)
- **%10 e2e** — Playwright, sadece kritik user journey'ler (6 tane MVP'de)

E2E %20'yi aşmamalı — yavaş, kırılgan, pahalı. Unit ≥%70 hedef.

## Bundle Size Budget — Frontend

- **Initial load**: ≤200 KB gzipped
- **Route chunks**: ≤150 KB gzipped each
- **Component lazy chunks**: ≤50 KB gzipped

`next.config.mjs` webpack performance hints ile enforce:

```javascript
config.performance = {
  hints: 'error',
  maxAssetSize: 200 * 1024,
  maxEntrypointSize: 250 * 1024,
};
```

Her PR'da `@next/bundle-analyzer` delta raporu:
- +10 KB altı: ok
- +10-50 KB: warning (reviewer decision)
- +50 KB üstü: block + justification gerekli

## Performance SLO (Production)

- **P50 response time**: <200ms
- **P95 response time**: <500ms
- **P99 response time**: <1000ms
- **Error rate (5xx)**: <0.1%
- **Uptime**: 99.5%

Web Vitals (frontend):
- **LCP** (Largest Contentful Paint): <2.5s
- **INP** (Interaction to Next Paint): <200ms
- **CLS** (Cumulative Layout Shift): <0.1

Lighthouse CI her PR'da kritik 3 sayfada çalışır:
- `/login` (unauthenticated)
- `/dashboard` (authenticated)
- `/processes` (büyük liste)

Eşikler:
- Performance ≥ 0.80
- Accessibility ≥ 0.90
- Best practices ≥ 0.90

## Linting & Type Checking

Her PR green olmalı:

- `pnpm lint` — ESLint (project config) + Prettier
- `pnpm typecheck` — TypeScript strict, `noUnusedLocals`, `noImplicitAny`

Lint warning'ler de fail olarak sayılır (`--max-warnings=0`).

## CI Pipeline Gate'leri (PR)

`.github/workflows/pr-check.yml` job'ları — hepsi green olmalı:

1. **lint** — ESLint + Prettier + TypeScript
2. **unit-test** — Vitest unit + coverage upload (Codecov)
3. **integration-test** — Docker PostgreSQL + Redis + Vitest integration
4. **security-scan** — Snyk (high+ blocks) + trufflehog (secret scan)
5. **build** — Turbo build + Next.js bundle analysis

Toplam süre hedefi: <8 dakika.

Branch protection: main'e merge için 1 approval + tüm gate'ler green + up-to-date branch.

## PR Merge Criteria

Merge button aktif olması için:

- [ ] CI tüm job'ları green
- [ ] En az 1 reviewer approval (security-critical için 2 — `/apps/api/src/auth/**`, `/apps/api/src/encryption/**`, `/apps/api/src/audit/**`)
- [ ] Branch main ile up-to-date
- [ ] Merge conflict yok
- [ ] All conversations resolved (review comments)

Squash merge only. Merge commit ve rebase merge disable.

## Accessibility Gate

WCAG 2.1 AA zorunlu. Manuel check'ler PR'da:

- [ ] Tüm interaktif element keyboard-accessible (Tab navigation)
- [ ] Focus visible (ring styling)
- [ ] Screen reader anlamlı (aria-label, aria-describedby, role)
- [ ] Form label'ları `<FormLabel>` içinde (shadcn aria-labelledby otomatik)
- [ ] Color contrast ≥ 4.5:1 (normal text), ≥ 3:1 (large text)
- [ ] Keyboard trap yok (modal'da focus loop çalışır, ESC ile çıkış)

axe-core integration test'lerde otomatik çalışır.

## Security Gate

- [ ] Dependency vulnerability: 0 HIGH+ (Snyk)
- [ ] Secret leak: trufflehog green
- [ ] Code security: Snyk Code HIGH+ block
- [ ] CSP strict: inline script sadece nonce'lu (Lighthouse best-practices ölçer)
- [ ] `dangerouslySetInnerHTML` yalnız DOMPurify sonrası (ESLint rule)

Nightly full scan:
- OWASP ZAP baseline (staging)
- Snyk full scan (transitive deps)
- Mutation testing (opsiyonel, haftalık — Stryker %60+ mutation score)

## Performance Gate (Ayrı Pipeline)

Haftalık/ayllık:
- k6 load test 1000 concurrent user — P95 <500ms, error <0.1%
- Lighthouse CI — scores eşikler altı ise warning

Production monitoring:
- CloudWatch dashboard: error rate, response time, DB CPU, Redis memory
- Sentry: exception tracking + Performance transactions

## Eşik Altında Kalırsa?

**Coverage düşüşü:** Reviewer trade-off değerlendirir. Legacy code simplify'dan geliyorsa ok. Yeni code test atlamışsa block.

**Bundle size artışı:** Gerekçelendir (yeni feature, kritik library) veya lazy-load et.

**Lighthouse performance dip:** Bottleneck tespit + fix. Deploy öncesi green zorunlu.

**Security scan finding:** Triage:
- HIGH/CRITICAL → immediate fix (block)
- MEDIUM → scheduled fix (next sprint)
- LOW → backlog
- False positive → Snyk ignore + justification

